body: Thank you L0lic0пwizard for the kind words, may I not forget this journey, and this journey not forget me. The road has no end so I only wish to keep sane through this path. May we see each other in the future.
May the hentai gods give you strength on your jurny MinaYaku, the road ahead is long and filled with many fantastic and terrible things.
